{"tid":2372024,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"721 一周年　被控襲警女學生　准保釋候訊","createTime":"2021-01-19T10:10:57.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-19T12:20:43.000Z","uid":56115,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"e61283ab4fc8b7b5434de71fb320a60e5a6722ea","tid":2372024,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-19T10:10:57.000Z","msg":"網民在元朗「721」事件一周年之時，發起「和你shop」行動，多人響應號召在元朗及附近商場聚集，結果被捕。事隔近半年，一名<span class=\"red\">年輕女學生被指襲警</span>，今午（ 19 日）在屯門裁判法院提訊。她暫時毋須答辯，案件押後至 3 月 16 日再訊，以便辯方索取警方文件及給予法律意見，其間女學生獲准以 1000 元保釋，同時須每週向警署報到。<br />\n<br />\n女被告馮**（ 18 歲，學生）被控於 2020 年 7 月 21 日在元朗舊墟路近燈柱 AD5167 ，故意阻撓正當執行職務的<span class=\"red\">女警員 26207 方子欣</span>。"},{"pid":"495a63a965e9ebb0ea029ebff793ac8fa1027d08","tid":2372024,"uid":56115,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-19T10:11:05.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/court/721-%E4%B8%80%E5%91%A8%E5%B9%B4-%E8%A2%AB%E6%8E%A7%E8%A5%B2%E8%AD%A6%E5%A5%B3%E5%AD%B8%E7%94%9F-%E5%87%86%E4%BF%9D%E9%87%8B%E5%80%99%E8%A8%8A/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fcourt%2F721-%25E4%25B8%2580%25E5%2591%25A8%25E5%25B9%25B4-%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%258E%25A7%25E8%25A5%25B2%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E5%25A5%25B3%25E5%25AD%25B8%25E7%2594%259F-%25E5%2587%2586%25E4%25BF%259D%25E9%2587%258B%25E5%2580%2599%25E8%25A8%258A%2F&d=CthjHxCXz%2Bl0vOF3eBkmepzZIytzq3Xhz5Kp58Ixet8%3D&h=4190f0aa\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fcourt%2F721-%25E4%25B8%2580%25E5%2591%25A8%25E5%25B9%25B4-%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%258E%25A7%25E8%25A5%25B2%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E5%25A5%25B3%25E5%25AD%25B8%25E7%2594%259F-%25E5%2587%2586%25E4%25BF%259D%25E9%2587%258B%25E5%2580%2599%25E8%25A8%258A%2F&h=046d253c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/court/721-%E4%B8%80%E5%91%A8%E5%B9%B4-%E8%A2%AB%E6%8E%A7%E8%A5%B2%E8%AD%A6%E5%A5%B3%E5%AD%B8%E7%94%9F-%E5%87%86%E4%BF%9D%E9%87%8B%E5%80%99%E8%A8%8A/</a>"},{"pid":"9830ecb0a486d